title: Help (1)
description:
Each page contains commands and their respective usages
Messages created by the bot will sometimes be reacted by the bot. Mostly, these reactions are interactable and trigger bot action.

fields.name: `event`
fields.value: Sends a private message to the user who prompted the command with an event configuration panel.

fields.name: `presence [time_minutes]`
fields.value:
`presence` returns all members currently in a voice channel.
`presence time_minutes` records presence over the given time.
